About:
Portfolio Solutions® has been offering low-cost passive investment solutions since 1999, and manages more than $1.5 billion* in client investment assets. We provide a full spectrum of wealth management and financial advisory services to our clients, utilizing our low-cost passive investing philosophy.
*AS OF 7/18/17
Meet the Team







Our mission statement







Portfolio Solutions® helps our clients achieve confidence in meeting their long-term financial goals by providing a full spectrum of wealth management and financial advisory services.
HOW WE HELP YOU INVEST WITH CONFIDENCE:
 
We offer multiple wealth management and financial advisory service levels, matched to your comfort level, stage and complexity in financial life
We provide a dedicated Financial Advisor and Client Relationship Management team
Our team includes in-house Certified Financial Planners, Chartered Financial Analysts, Master’s Degree holders, a CPA, and an attorney/former FBI Special Agent
You receive regular reviews and updates regarding your financial situation
We provide daily asset allocation monitoring and rebalancing with strategies that minimize trading costs
We construct portfolios effectively diversified to spread risk across up to 10 asset classes comprised of more than 31,000 securities
You select an independent custodian. Portfolio Solutions® has no access to your investment assets (except for payment of management fees), only trading authority in accordance with your long-term investment strategy. All of your investment assets are held at an independent third party custodian of your choice.
We provide account transfer and implementation services
We provide a secure online client portal for digital storage of your important documents and daily portfolio tracking & quarterly performance reports
We offer tax loss harvesting & tax management services
We provide income distribution projections for assets managed by Portfolio Solutions®

WE'RE HERE FOR YOU THROUGH ALL STAGES OF YOUR FINANCIAL JOURNEY

 
Portfolio Solutions At A Glance

Corporate Headquarters

Troy, Michigan

Founded

1999

Total Client Assets Under Management

More than $1.5 billion*

Service Offerings

Wealth Management
Financial Planning
Investment Guidance

Number of Employees

18

SEC Registration

Portfolio Solutions® is registered as an investment advisor with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission.  Registration does not imply a certain level of skill or training.

Fast Facts

Low-cost investment philosophy, using index funds, that seeks to capture the returns of the entire market (passive investing)
Fiduciary standard – Portfolio Solutions® must act in the best interest of its clients at all times as a Registered Investment Advisor (RIA) regulated by the US. Securities and Exchange Commission
Years of experience and discipline that comes with working with more than 600 clients and their nearly 2,000 individual investment accounts on a daily basis

Phone

248-689-1550     800-448-3550

Mailing Address

900 Wilshire Dr, Suite 200
					Troy, MI 48084


