UNDER 
	MANAGEMENT*







WE ARE: FINANCIAL ADVISORS FOCUSED ON YOUR NEEDS.








 


EXPERIENCE: We work with hundreds of clients and maintain over $1.5 billion in assets under management*, including high net worth families, trusts, and non-profit organizations throughout the United States.
FULL SERVICE: We provide wealth planning and management services based on individual client needs, delivered by our team of experienced and credentialed professionals.
FIDUCIARY STANDARD: As a Registered Investment Advisor with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, we place the financial interests of our clients ahead of our own at all times**.
TRANSPARENCY: We are an independent firm and do not receive commissions. We earn fees only as a percentage of the assets placed under our management. All client assets are held by an independent qualified custodian such as Charles Schwab & Co., Inc. or TD Ameritrade, Inc.
                 More Details
**  SEC registration does not constitute an endorsement of the firm by the SEC, nor does it indicate that the advisor has attained a particular level of skill or ability.







WE DO: SENSIBLE SOLUTIONS. 











 


The root of investment success is a sound philosophy which forms the foundation for creating a custom strategy and developing the discipline to stick with it. Our philosophy is that the global financial markets provide good returns, and attempts to beat the markets results mostly in lower returns. High fees and poor investment selection create barriers to success, and tax costs can be a major detriment to return.  We strive to recognize, address and mitigate all these costs at Portfolio Solutions®.
Index Investing                 Low Fees








The stock market serves as a relocation center at which money is moved from the active to the patient.
-Warren Buffett








